snippet.title: Neurocracy Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
NEUROCRACY is a sci-fi hypertext game that invites you to explore the Wikipedia of the year 2049. Then a murder happens and the editing war begins! Find clues, draw connections, compare notes with others, and solve the murder across ten episodes

Check it out for zero money at https://omnipedia.app

Website: https://neurocracy.site
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Neurocracy2049
Discord: https://discord.gg/9ghXDan
Developer: https://playthroughline.com

Trailer music by Virlyn: https://virlyn.bandcamp.com
Trailer edit by Game If You Are: https://gameifyouare.com

Note: this trailer shows placeholder stock art. The full version of Neurocracy features artwork from Alice Duke (http://alice-duke.com)
